Please be aware, the District reserves the right to remove content posted to, or within the comment sections of, the District’s social media that:

• Is off-topic;
• Contains personal attacks;
• Contains spam;
• Contains discriminatory, defamatory, obscene, profane, or harassing language;
• Contains confidential information;
• Violates the property rights of others (such as when an account is hacked or used by another person, or violates copyright laws).

